{
  "stem": "280.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But their oldest daughter was taken by her parents to be-- to be brought up in Slovakia and Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she went to school in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was perfect German and Slovak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was elected to work in the office, the [GERMAN], it's called.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is writing, [GERMAN] is room in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she had knowledge of these transports, when they are gonna be and where they are going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were-- there was some information where you are taken and what kind of work these-- these people are taken to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So through her help, we got-- she maneuvered that we should be in that transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We should be selected in this transport, which went to the town, which was considered a very good transport, a very good labor camp, because you didn't have to work outdoors.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an aeroplane factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now, again, retrack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the selection processes in Auschwitz, those who were not fit by Mengele were pulled out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were locked in and-- I have to interject again something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each block, each barrack of this was-- was managed by two girls, Jewish girls, but Jewish girls from Slovakia, who unfortunately were in Auschwitz many years before.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were already trained by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to work along with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how they survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were the ones who were in actual contact with us as to what to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- So she had a-- like a little office, a little room of her own in-- in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in open, you know, but she had a little room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So during these selections, the ones which Mengele found not fit were thrown into this little room, and then later taken, you know, to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
